Sockets

status
url : wss://localhost:2500/ws/status/<str:token>/<int:type>
type : {1 : 'ONLINE', 2 : IN_GAME}
onclose | onerror : type becomes automatically OFFLINE


block-unblock

url : wss://localhost:2500/ws/block-unblock/${token}
data : 
{'action': 'block', 'blocked': '2'}
{'action': 'unblock', 'blocked': '2'}

FriendshipRequest : 
url : ws/friend-reqs/<str:token>
data:
{'action': 'accept', 'friend': 1}
{'action': 'create', 'friend': 1}
{'action': 'deny', 'friend': 1}
